'''Imoh Umoren''' (wavutse ku ya 13 Kanama 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime [[Nijeriya|wo]] muri [[Nigeriya]] ukora cyane cyane firime zo mu Buhinde<ref>https://independent.ng/filmmaker-imoh-umoren-recounts-close-shave-with-covid-19/</ref> .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa film ya 2017 ''Abana b'ibyondo'' . Umoren afatwa nkumukinnyi wa mbere wakoze firime wicecekeye wumukara numweru mubikorwa bya firime ya Nollywood.<ref>https://www.kweli.tv/authors/imoh-umoren?locale=en</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 13 Kanama 1982 muri [[Nijeriya]]. Se yari umunyapolitiki naho nyina yari umwarimu wa kaminuza.<ref>https://thisisafrica.me/arts-and-culture/how-nollywood-filmmakers-are-coping-with-the-pandemic/</ref>  Umoren avuga ko nyina yagize uruhare mu mwuga we wo gukina filime. Ababyeyi be bombi bapfuye akiri ingimbi, kandi yarezwe na bene wabo kugeza ubwo yikubise wenyine afite imyaka 16<ref>https://motherhoodinstyle.net/tag/imoh-umoren/</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 9, Umoren yatangiye kwandika urukurikirane rusekeje rwitwa ''The Wickeds'' hamwe ninshuti ye magara Richie<ref>https://www.gistlover.com/imoh-umoren-reveals-how-someone-stole-his-idea-for-a-movie-and-invited-him-to-the-premiere/</ref>. Yinjiye nka producer muto muri 'Common Ground Production' kandi akora kumurongo mpuzamahanga witwa ''The Station'' <ref>https://www.ghgossip.com/my-life-aint-pretty-but-my-lady-is-imoh-umoren-laud-praises-on-wife/</ref>.  Nyuma, yinjiye mubikorwa bya TV bya francise nka ''Project Fame'', ''MTV yo kuburira mbere'', ''Ntuzibagirwe Amagambo'' ''n'imbyino za Street Guinness''<ref>https://www.lekismedia.com.ng/imoh-umoren-biography-and-net-worth/</ref> . 

Afite imyaka 26, yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana ''Lemon Green''  Filime yamenyekanye cyane. Hanyuma muri 2010, yayoboye film ngufi ''All Sorts Of Trouble'' . Muri 2013, filime ye ya TV Yagize ''Umunsi'' mwiza yatowe nka Cinematografi nziza.<ref>https://moviefit.me/persons/1021048-imoh-umoren</ref><ref>https://movierad.com/en/person/2502378-imoh-umoren</ref> Muri 2015 yayoboye firime black and white silent movie ''Hard Times'', imutsindira AMVCA yambere.  Kuri filime ye y’ibyago ''The Happyness Limited'', umukinnyi wa mbere Tope Tedela yatowe nkumukinnyi mwiza muri [[Afurika]] muri Afrika Magic Viewers 'Choice Awards (AMVCA)<ref>https://www.nairagent.com/tag/imoh-umoren/</ref>. 

Umoren yaje kwandika no kuyobora film yamamaye cyane''Children of Mud'' ishingiye ku nkuru ifatika<ref>https://www.pulse.ng/lifestyle/food-travel/mcm-filmmaker-imoh-umoren-is-our-man-crush-this-monday/zk5dhkm</ref>.  Filime yakiriye nomination 7 mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime zitandukanye zirimo:[[:en:Nigeria_Entertainment_Awards|Nigeria Entertainment Awards]] (NEA) na AMVCA.  Filime ye y'ibyago yakurikiyeho ''Dear Bayo'' yerekanwe mu birori 11 bya firime kandi yatsindiye ibihembo 6 mu iserukiramuco rya Nollywood mu [[Bwongereza]] andi maserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ya firime.  Umoren yayoboye kandi filime ''Lagos:'' ''Sex, Lies & Traffic'' yafatanije na Gbemisola Afolabi<ref>https://independent.ng/filmmaker-imoh-umoren-recounts-close-shave-with-covid-19/</ref>.

Nyuma yarangije gutunganya ikinamico yigihe ''The Herbert Macaulay Affair'', biopic ivuga kuri Herbert Macaulay, muri 2018.   Muri 2020, yakoze urukurikirane rw'ikinamico ''Umuyoboro wa 77''<ref>https://nollytrailers.com/news/imoh-umoren-starts-a-new-epoch-with-his-intriguing-lagos-sex-lies-and-traffic/</ref> . 

